Problem statement
Given an array of length N, you need to find and return the sum of all elements of the array.

Do this recursively.

Detailed explanation ( Input/output format, Notes, Images )
Constraints :
1 <= N <= 10^3
Sample Input 1 :
3
9 8 9
Sample Output 1 :
26
Sample Input 2 :
3
4 2 1
Sample Output 2 :
7    

//code
int sum(int input[], int n) {
    if (n == 0)
        return 0;
    return input[n - 1] + sum(input, n - 1);
}
